String note at any fret:
  E string: E(0) F(1) F#(2) G(3) G#(4) A(5) A#(6) B(7) C(8) C#(9) D(10) D#(11) E(12)
  A string: A(0) A#(1) B(2) C(3) C#(4) D(5) D#(6) E(7) F(8) F#(9) G(10) G#(11) A(12)
